highlights.description: Journalist talking about the benefits of LVN for newsrooms with limited budget.
Journalist talking about the power of LVN's search capabilities.
Journalist underscoring the value of being able to listen to authentic and personal conversations.
Cap Times journalists introduce themselves and explain their values
Working with Alex Gee on his Cap Times essay and then listening, and having her eyes opened
Hopes for the ways LVN can help us understand where people are coming from
I want journalism to enable people to hear voices that may not be the ones in their immediate lives
Journalist says this suspicion about the news media is frustrating because we are passionate about what we do and want our reporting to be seen as the professional work that it is
Reporting commenting on the value of hearing a highlight from another conversation
I like when people contact me as a reporter with a story idea, and highlight something I didn't know about
Reporters' concern over lack of trust in the news, especially in recent years
Reporter wanting his stories to speak to a broad audience, doing an audit of his sources
As a journalist of color, it is a tough balance to make sure your journalism is impactful while recognizing the issues we face won't be solved by one article
Managing editor feeling urgency around the business model underneath some media organizations
As a journalists, I never take it lightly when someone shares their personal story with me
Journalist saying that what excites him about LVN is that people are having more thoughtful and intentional discourse
Journalist saying that LVN yields a more organic conversation, a different conversation than if he were in the room
Journalists saying that LVN can yield different topics, enable them to hear from people who don't have publicists
Journalists talking about how they strive to include many points of people, under-represented voices
Listening in to conversations allows you to understand what the dynamic is, without your presence as a journalist.
It is just a very beautiful city
I love the community festivals, like the Grilled Cheese competition
